<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Our history</strong></h2>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">How Meeting Tomorrow began.</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">Our founder, Mark Aistrope, used to be a traveling sales rep. Locating and setting up AV equipment around the country was a major hassle, and he was sick of spending too much time and energy dealing with logistics and tech problems. Mark knew there had to be a better way. It came to him when he was putting a Netflix DVD in the mail.</p>

<h3 style="text-align: left;">The "Aha!" moment.</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">Netflix for projectors! Our founder, Mark, started with 15 projectors and a website that allowed him to ship back and forth across the country. He also recruited a network of trusted technicians and was able to provide professional set up and assistance anywhere in the US.</p>

<h3 style="text-align: left;">Where we are today.</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">Those 15 projectors are now part of a distribution warehouse with the latest presentation equipment: everything from iPads to plasmas, to stages. And Meeting Tomorrow is now a growing team of 70 customer-focused employees and many, many happy customers.</p>

<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Customer reviews</strong></h2>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">What people are saying.</h3>
